headline: Jim Cramer Dissects Kimberly-Clark’s Acquisition of Kenvue
summary: Kimberly-Clark Corporation (NASDAQ:KMB) is one of the stocks Jim Cramer recently offered insights on. Cramer discussed the company’s planned acquisition of Kenvue during the episode.
